            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>禮來(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LLY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LLY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LLY-US</a>)截至台北時間01日21:41股價上漲47.97美元，報982.57美元，漲幅5.13%，成交量611,037（股），盤中最高價982.57美元、最低價943.80美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.31%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.71%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.06%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>禮來(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LLY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LLY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LLY-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.85%</li> <li>近 1 月：+5.41%</li> <li>近 3 月：-9.89%</li> <li>近 6 月：+10.67%</li> <li>今年以來：-13.03%</li></ul></section></main>",
